<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idd1520038-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e" identifier="/us/usc/t50/s1909"><num value="1909">§ 1909.</num><heading> Fiscal year 1992 funding</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idd1520039-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e" identifier="/us/usc/t50/s1909/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Authorization of appropriations to Fund</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is hereby authorized to be appropriated to the Fund for fiscal year 1992 the sum of $150,000,000.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idd152003a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e" identifier="/us/usc/t50/s1909/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Authorization of obligations from Fund</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">During fiscal year 1992, there may be obligated from the Fund such amounts as may be provided in appropriations Acts, not to exceed $35,000,000. Amounts made available for obligation from the Fund for fiscal year 1992 shall remain available until expended.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idd152003b-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/183/tVIII/s809">Pub. L. 102–183, title VIII, § 809</ref>, <date date="1991-12-04">Dec. 4, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/1277">105 Stat. 1277</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
